# brand-sites

- Git repo name: **brand-sites**. Apps live in `apps/*`; shared code in `packages/*` as **`@publication-websites/*`** (npm scope).
- Do not import one app from another app.
- Do not add BigQuery or unauthenticated email-based subscription lookup to marketing Next apps; use magic `/api/reader-subscriptions` with Bearer token.
- Prefer env-driven brand config in each app’s `src/config/site.js`.
- See root `AGENTS.md` and `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`.
